          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Expedited Disability Insurance Payments for Terminally Ill Individuals Act of 2015 </b></p> <p> Amends title II (Old Age, Survivors and Disability Insurance) of the Social Security Act to prescribe formulae for payment of Social Security Disability Insurance benefits over a period of 24 consecutive calendar months for individuals determined to be under a disability upon submission of a diagnosis of a terminal illness.</p>]]></text>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
